================================================================================
P0 RENDER GRAPH EXECUTION FIX - MANUAL APPLICATION REQUIRED
================================================================================

FILE: src/rendering/Renderer.ts
LOCATION: Line ~557-564 (in the render() method)

ISSUE: RenderGraph is compiled but never executed - all advanced render passes
(SSAO, SSR, SSGI, Volumetric) are bypassed.

================================================================================
FIND AND REPLACE:
================================================================================

FIND THIS CODE (lines ~557-564):
-----------------------------------
    // Render scene meshes directly (bypasses render graph for now)
    if (this.profiler) {
      this.profiler.beginPass('Scene Meshes');
    }
    this.renderSceneMeshes(scene, camera);
    if (this.profiler) {
      this.profiler.endPass();
    }


REPLACE WITH:
-----------------------------------
    // Execute render graph if compiled, fallback to direct rendering
    if (this.profiler) {
      this.profiler.beginPass('Scene Rendering');
    }

    if (this.renderGraph && this.renderGraph.isCompiled()) {
      // Use render graph execution for all advanced passes (SSAO, SSR, SSGI, Volumetric, etc.)
      this.renderGraph.execute(scene, camera);
    } else {
      // Fallback to direct mesh rendering if render graph not available
      logger.warn('Render graph not compiled, using direct rendering fallback');
      this.renderSceneMeshes(scene, camera);
    }

    if (this.profiler) {
      this.profiler.endPass();
    }


================================================================================
WHY THIS FIX IS NEEDED:
================================================================================

1. The RenderGraph is built and compiled in initialize() (line 345-346)
2. But the render() method bypasses it completely (line 612 → now 561)
3. This means ALL render passes added to the graph never execute:
   - DepthPrePass
   - ShadowPass
   - GBufferPass
   - LightingPass
   - SkyboxPass
   - ForwardPass (for transparents)
   - Any future advanced passes

4. The fix adds conditional execution:
   - If render graph is compiled → execute it (enables all passes)
   - If not compiled → fallback to direct rendering (safe)

================================================================================
VERIFICATION:
