After applying the fix, you should see:
✓ this.renderGraph.execute(scene, camera) is called
✓ RenderGraph.isCompiled() check is present
✓ Fallback to renderSceneMeshes() if graph not ready
✓ Warning logged when using fallback path

Methods used exist in RenderGraph.ts:
✓ isCompiled(): boolean (line 233)
✓ execute(scene?: any, camera?: any): void (line 440)

